OL,3,CJersey Airport's Director of
OL,4,COperations resigns
OL,6,FThe Director of Operations at Jersey
OL,7,FAirport has resigned after 17 months
OL,8,Fin the role.
OL,10,FAshley Maggs joined Ports in 2014,
OL,11,Fstarting with the Airport's Rescue and
OL,12,FFire Fighting Service before advancing
OL,13,Fto Deputy Director and then Director
OL,14,Fof Operations upon the retirement of
OL,15,FRobin MacRae at the end of February
OL,16,F2024.
