OL,3,CJersey Airport's Director of
OL,4,COperations resigns
OL,6,FHe is described by Ports as the
OL,7,F"accountable manager for the Airport"
OL,8,Fand is often the public face for
OL,9,Fsharing information during key events,
OL,10,Fsuch as March's bomb threat that saw
OL,11,Fthe terminal evacuated and the lifting
OL,12,Fof 'special attention' measures.
OL,14,FIn an email from Mr Maggs to all
OL,15,Fairport staff and seen by ITV News, he
OL,16,Fsays: "After much reflection and
OL,17,Fconsideration, I have made the
OL,18,Fdecision to resign.
