OL,3,CJersey Airport's Director of
OL,4,COperations resigns
OL,6,F"I am proud of what we've achieved
OL,7,Ftogether, what we've delivered, and
OL,8,Fthe teamwork that defines us,
OL,9,Fespecially when faced with challenges."
OL,11,FIn a statement, Ports says: "After 11
OL,12,Fyears at Ports of Jersey, Ashley
OL,13,FMaggs, Airport Director, tendered his
OL,14,Fresignation this week.
OL,16,F"Business continues as usual as Ashley
OL,17,Fworks his six-month notice period and
OL,18,Frecruitment has already begun for a
OL,19,Fsuccessor.
