OL,3,CJersey Airport's Director of
OL,4,COperations resigns
OL,6,F"Ashley has been a key member of our
OL,7,Fteam for more than a decade and a
OL,8,Ffantastic colleague; it's safe to say
OL,9,Fwe are going to miss him."
OL,11,FFollowing speculation that Ports'
OL,12,FChief Executive Officer, Matt Thomas,
OL,13,Fmay also be stepping down, the group
OL,14,Fconfirms that he has "no plans to
OL,15,Fleave" and adds his expertise is key
OL,16,Fas the airport and harbour undergo
OL,17,Fmajor upgrades.
